title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Feb 24 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Feb 24 2022
description:
We're witnessing the high price of the Biden presidency: Russia launches major invasion of Ukraine. Buck says, "Only military could go toe-to-toe with Russia are our own and Chinese. After that, I think they could take any European power pretty handily on their own, not all at once. But this is major." Will China make a move on Taiwan? Clay has been predicting it for days already. John Kerry worries about climate change as Putin invades Ukraine, Democrats worry about unvaccinated Ukrainians hiding in closed rooms. Psaki on inflation: "Standing up for our values is not without cost.” Fear of U.S. getting sucked into a conflict we want no part of. How much is Putin willing to lose?
